---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout 
  title="Location & Access" 
  description="Located in Awaji 1-chome area, Osaka. 1 stop from Shin-Osaka station via train, easy access from KIX airport."
>
  <div class="container page-content">
    <h1>Location & Access</h1>
    <p class="text-ja mb-xl">所在地・アクセス</p>
    
    <section class="mb-xl">
      <h2>Address Area</h2>
      <p class="text-ja mb-sm">住所エリア</p>
      <div class="info-box">
        <p><strong>Awaji 1-chome area, Higashiyodogawa-ku, Osaka</strong></p>
        <p class="text-ja">大阪府大阪市東淀川区淡路1丁目付近</p>
        <p class="text-muted mt-sm" style="font-size: 0.9em;">
          * The full exact address and check-in instructions are provided via Airbnb after booking is confirmed.<br/>
          <span class="text-ja">* 正確な詳細住所およびチェックイン方法は、ご予約確定後にAirbnbのメッセージでご案内いたします。</span>
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-xl">
      <h2>Nearest Stations</h2>
      <p class="text-ja mb-sm">最寄り駅</p>
      <ul class="access-list">
        <li>
          <strong>Higashi-Yodogawa Station (JR Kyoto Line)</strong>
          <div class="text-ja">JR京都線「東淀川駅」</div>
          <p class="route-note">Very convenient! Only 1 stop from Shin-Osaka bulk train station.</p>
          <p class="text-ja text-muted">新幹線「新大阪駅」からわずか1駅と大変便利です。</p>
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Awaji Station (Hankyu Line / Osaka Metro Sakaisuji Line)</strong>
          <div class="text-ja">阪急電鉄・Osaka Metro堺筋線「淡路駅」</div>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-xl">
      <h2>From Major Airports & Stations</h2>
      <p class="text-ja mb-sm">主要な空港・駅からのアクセス</p>
      
      <div class="route-card">
        <h3>From Kansai International Airport (KIX)</h3>
        <p class="text-ja mb-sm">関西国際空港からのルート</p>
        <div class="route-steps">
          <span class="step">KIX</span>
          <span class="arrow">→ (Train: Haruka Express) →</span>
          <span class="step">Shin-Osaka Sta.</span>
          <span class="arrow">→ (Train: JR Kyoto Line, 1 stop) →</span>
          <span class="step">Higashi-Yodogawa Sta.</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="route-card mt-md">
        <h3>From Shin-Osaka Station by Taxi</h3>
        <p class="text-ja mb-sm">新大阪駅からタクシーをご利用の場合</p>
        <p>Approximately 4 minutes by taxi from Shin-Osaka station.</p>
        <p class="text-ja">新大阪駅からタクシーで約4分です。</p>
      </div>
    </section>

  </div>
</Layout>

<style>
  .page-content {
    padding: var(--spacing-xl) var(--spacing-sm);
  }
  .mb-xl {
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-xl);
  }
  .mt-sm {
    margin-top: var(--spacing-sm);
  }
  .mt-md {
    margin-top: var(--spacing-md);
  }
  .info-box {
    background: var(--color-bg-alt);
    padding: var(--spacing-lg);
    border-radius: 8px;
    border-left: 4px solid var(--color-brand);
  }
  .access-list {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
  }
  .access-list li {
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-lg);
  }
  .route-note {
    font-size: 0.95em;
    color: var(--color-brand);
    margin-top: 4px;
  }
  .route-card {
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    padding: var(--spacing-md);
    border-radius: 8px;
  }
  .route-steps {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 8px;
    background: var(--color-bg-alt);
    padding: var(--spacing-md);
    border-radius: 6px;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
  }
  .step {
    font-weight: bold;
  }
  .arrow {
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    font-size: 0.85em;
  }
</style>
